'''陳國治'''（{{lang|en|Michael Chan}}；{{bd|1951年||||}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]]的親中国政治人物，[[安大略自由黨|安大略自由黨]]前黨員，2007-18年間任[[安大略省|安大略省]][[安大略省省議會|省議員]]，先後代表{{tsl|en|Markham (provincial electoral district)|萬錦選區 (省選)|萬錦選區}}及{{tsl|en|Markham—Unionville (provincial electoral district)|萬錦於人村選區 (省選)|萬錦於人村}}（Markham—Unionville）[[選區|選區]]，在[[道爾頓·麥堅迪|麥堅迪]]及[[凱斯琳·韋恩|韋恩]]執政期間期間曾先後出任安省稅務廳長、旅遊及文化廳長、[[2015年泛美運動會|2015年泛美運動會]]事務廳長、公民及移民廳長和國際貿易廳長，為該省歷來第二位華裔内閣廳長<ref name="51a"/>。陳國治曾經是[[旺市|旺市]]一家知名律師事務所{{tsl|en|Miller Thomson LLP||Miller Thomson LLP}}的高級商業顧問<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/canada/british-columbia/article-former-ontario-minister-sides-with-beijing-pins-hong-kong-protests-on/|title=Former Ontario minister sides with Beijing, pins Hong Kong protests on ‘outside' forces|website=The Globe and Mail|language=en-US|access-date=2019-10-10|archive-date=2019-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190916032451/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/canada/british-columbia/article-former-ontario-minister-sides-with-beijing-pins-hong-kong-protests-on/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，他亦是{{tsl|en|Seneca College of Applied Arts and Technology||Seneca College of Applied Arts and Technology}}的董事局成員<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.millerthomson.com/en/our-people/michael-chan/|title=Michael Chan|website=Miller Thomson LLP|language=en-US|access-date=2019-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214233334/https://www.millerthomson.com/en/our-people/michael-chan/|archive-date=2019-02-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==簡歷==
===早年生活===
陳國治於[[广州|广州]]出生，父親為[[中國國民黨|國民黨]]官員<ref name = "MMC"/>。[[國共内戰|國共内戰]]後一家先後遷居[[澳門|澳門]]和[[香港|香港]]<ref name = "MMC"/>{{r|gcp}}。1969年，18歲的陳國治移居加拿大<ref>{{cite news |author=震濤 |title=陳國治：酒香也怕巷子深 “唱好”安省只争朝夕 |url=http://fameweekly.com/a/tebiebaodao/2011/0808/26.html |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315193304/http://fameweekly.com/a/tebiebaodao/2011/0808/26.html |work= |publisher=《名人名商周刊》 |date=2011-08-08 |access-date=2012-02-10 |archive-date=2012-03-15}}</ref><ref name = "ET1">{{cite news|last= Ghoreishi|first= Omid|title= Ontario Minister Asked Festival to Ban Newspaper to Please Chinese Consul, Says Source|url= http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/canada/ontario-minister-asked-festival-to-ban-newspaper-to-please-chinese-consul-source-62163.html|newspaper= [[大纪元时报|The Epoch Times]]|location= |date= 2011-09-28|access-date= 2015-02-22|language= en|archive-date= 2015-02-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150222140229/http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/canada/ontario-minister-asked-festival-to-ban-newspaper-to-please-chinese-consul-source-62163.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

移居加拿大後，陳國治與中國大陸依然保持着緊密的聯繫：根據一篇於2008年由[[新华社|新华社]]進行的訪問，陳國治在1980年代初期曾頻密地訪問中國大陸超過70次{{r|ET1}}。他這樣對記者說：「嚴格來說，我是個加拿大人，但我時常都關注我在文化上的根源。所以我很關心中國的事務<ref name = "ET1"/>。」從1995年開始，陳國治於萬錦市定居。

陳國治在加拿大從事保險業。
在進入政壇之前，他曾擔任由[[加拿大自由党|聯邦自由黨]]的[[麥家廉|麥家廉]]出任議員的萬錦選區協會主席。

==政治生涯==
原萬錦選區省議員{{tsl|en|Tony Wong (Canadian politician)|黃志華}}於2006年為了參與[[約克區|約克區]]區議會選舉而辭去其[[安大略省省議會|安大略省省議會]]議席後，陳國治於[[2007年安大略省補選|2007年2月8日舉行的補選]]代表省自由黨參與該議席，並壓倒省保守黨候選人[[袁海耀|袁海耀]]贏得該議席<ref name=gcp>{{cite news |author= |title=香港移民陳國治出任安省稅務廳長 |url=http://www.gcpnews.com/zh-tw/articles/2007-02-21/C1023_6377.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108184940/http://gcpnews.com/zh-tw/articles/2007-02-21/C1023_6377.html |publisher=《[[環球華報|環球華報]]》 |date=2007-02-21 |archivedate=2009-01-08 |accessdate=2017-07-25 |language=zh |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。他於同年2月21日獲[[安大略省省長|安大略省省長]][[道爾頓·麥堅迪|麥堅迪]]委任入内閣，成為自1993年時任省長[[李博_(政治人物)|李博]]精簡内閣架構後首位省稅務廳長<ref>[http://www.premier.gov.on.ca/news/Product.asp?ProductID=974 Premier of Ontario - News Releases - Michael Chan Becomes Ontario's Minister Of Revenue]{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

他於2007年10月舉行的{{tsl|en|2007 Ontario general election|2007年安大略省大選|安省大選}}中順利連任<ref name="2007 results">{{cite web|url=http://elections.on.ca/NR/rdonlyres/AB409CCD-84F3-46FA-B3BD-39AB659EFC2D/0/SummaryofValidBallotsCastforEachCandidate.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091007160233/http://www.elections.on.ca/NR/rdonlyres/AB409CCD-84F3-46FA-B3BD-39AB659EFC2D/0/SummaryofValidBallotsCastforEachCandidate.pdf |dead-url=yes |archive-date=October 7, 2009 |title=Summary of Valid Ballots Cast for Each Candidate |publisher=Elections Ontario |date=October 10, 2007 |accessdate=2014-03-02 }}</ref>，並調任省公民及移民廳長，再於2010年1月調任省旅遊及文化廳長<ref>{{cite news |author= |title=加安省內閣改組 陳國治調任旅遊及文化廳長 |url=http://www.chinareviewnews.com/doc/1012/0/3/8/101203862.html?coluid=0&kindid=0&docid=101203862&mdate=0120102929 |work= |publisher=《中國評論新聞》 |date=2010-01-20 |accessdate=2012-02-10 }}</ref>。在2011年10月舉行的{{tsl|en|2011 Ontario general election|2011年安大略省大選|省選}}中，他再度連任<ref name="2011 results">{{cite web|url=http://elections.on.ca/NR/rdonlyres/7849B894-4C4F-490E-9E8C-271BCF0C0D4D/5712/SummaryofvalidvotescastforeacndGE2011.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130330163815/http://elections.on.ca/NR/rdonlyres/7849B894-4C4F-490E-9E8C-271BCF0C0D4D/5712/SummaryofvalidvotescastforeacndGE2011.pdf |dead-url=yes |archive-date=March 30, 2013 |title=Summary of Valid Ballots Cast for Each Candidate |publisher=Elections Ontario |date=October 6, 2011 |accessdate=2014-03-02 }}</ref>，並留任省旅遊及文化廳長一職<ref name="51a">{{cite news |author=葛健生 |title=4度入阁 陈国治：历任三个厅的华裔厅长 |url=http://info.51.ca/news/canada/2011/10/21/237926.shtml |work= |publisher=《世界新闻网》 |date=2011-10-21 |access-date=2012-02-10 |archive-date=2011-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111230085804/http://info.51.ca/news/canada/2011/10/21/237926.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，再於2012年11月加任2015年泛美運動會事務廳長，並從同月至2013年2月之間短暫復任公民及移民廳長<ref>{{cite web |title=MPP Michael Chan |url=http://www.ontla.on.ca/web/members/members_all_detail.do?locale=en&ID=7065 |publisher=[[安大略省省議會|安大略省省議會]] |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208100745/http://www.ontla.on.ca/web/members/members_all_detail.do?locale=en&ID=7065 |archive-date=2015-12-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他於2014年6月{{tsl|en|2014 Ontario general election|2014年安大略省大選|省選}}中順利連任<ref name="2014 results">{{cite web |title=General Election by District: Markham-Unionville |publisher=Elections Ontario |date=2014-06-12 |url=http://wemakevotingeasy.ca/en/general-election-district-results.aspx?d=046 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702073618/http://wemakevotingeasy.ca/en/general-election-district-results.aspx?d=046 |archivedate=2014-07-02 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author= |title=加安省內閣改組 陳國治調任旅遊及文化廳長 |url=http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/2014-06-13/headline1402649560d5096079.html |work= |publisher=《星島日報》加東版 |date=2014-06-13 |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618222305/http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/2014-06-13/headline1402649560d5096079.html |archive-date=2014-06-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，同月在新組成的内閣中調回公民、移民及國際貿易廳長職位<ref>{{cite news |author= |title=仿與科圖對調職位 陳國治三掌移民廳不言易 |url=http://www.mingpaotor.com/htm/News/20140625/taa1.htm?m=0 |work= |publisher=《明報》加東版 |date=2014-06-25 |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archive-date=2014-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703054556/http://www.mingpaotor.com/htm/News/20140625/taa1.htm?m=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

省長[[凱斯琳·韋恩|韋恩]]於2016年6月改組內閣，分拆公民及移民廳長和國際貿易廳長職務，陳國治留任國際貿易廳長<ref>{{cite news |author= |title=Kathleen Wynne's shuffled cabinet features 40% women |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/ontario-cabinet-changes-1.3632476 |work= |publisher=CBC News |date=2016-06-13 |access-date=2018-09-14 |archive-date=2018-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180327155339/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/ontario-cabinet-changes-1.3632476 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author= |title=出任國際貿易廳長 陳國治：駕輕就熟 |url=http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/938461/2016-06-14/post-%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%BB%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%BB%B3%E9%95%B7-%E9%99%B3%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%BB%EF%BC%9A%E9%A7%95%E8%BC%95%E5%B0%B1%E7%86%9F/?variant=zh-hk |work= |publisher=《星島日報》加東版 |date=2016-06-14 |access-date=2018-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180914205040/http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/938461/2016-06-14/post-%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%BB%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%BB%B3%E9%95%B7-%E9%99%B3%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%BB%EF%BC%9A%E9%A7%95%E8%BC%95%E5%B0%B1%E7%86%9F/?variant=zh-hk |archive-date=2018-09-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2018年4月，他宣布以個人健康為由，決定不會在同年6月舉行的{{tsl|en|2018 Ontario general election|2018年安大略省選舉|省選}}中競逐連任省議員<ref>{{cite news |author= |title=陳國治正式宣布：將不再尋求選舉連任 |url=http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/2485310/2018-04-05/post-%E9%99%B3%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%BB%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB/?variant=zh-hk |work= |publisher=《星島日報》加東版 |date=2018-04-05 |access-date=2018-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915003224/http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/2485310/2018-04-05/post-%E9%99%B3%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%BB%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB/?variant=zh-hk |archive-date=2018-09-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author= |title=陳國治健康為由不連任 安省自由黨再3人退出省選 |url=http://m.singtao.ca/calgary_hk_st/4-%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B/997140-%E9%99%B3%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%BB%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%e2%80%82%E5%AE%89%E7%9C%81%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E5%86%8D3%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E7%9C%81%E9%81%B8/ |work= |publisher=《星島日報》加東版 |date=2018-04-06 |accessdate=2018-09-14 |archive-date=2018-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915001724/http://m.singtao.ca/calgary_hk_st/4-%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B/997140-%E9%99%B3%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%BB%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%e2%80%82%E5%AE%89%E7%9C%81%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E5%86%8D3%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E7%9C%81%E9%81%B8/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="retire">{{cite news| url=https://www.thestar.com/news/queenspark/2018/04/05/liberal-cabinet-ministers-michael-chan-and-tracy-maccharles-mpp-grant-crack-say-they-are-retiring.html| title=Liberal cabinet ministers Michael Chan and Tracy MacCharles, MPP Grant Crack say they are retiring| first=Robert| last=Benzie| date=2018-04-05| publisher=[[多倫多星報|Toronto Star]]| language=en| accessdate=2019-08-12| archive-date=2018-04-05| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180405192305/https://www.thestar.com/news/queenspark/2018/04/05/liberal-cabinet-ministers-michael-chan-and-tracy-maccharles-mpp-grant-crack-say-they-are-retiring.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

